# Development Workflow Rules

All code generation must follow **Architecture v3 workflow**.

Spec
↓
State Model
↓
UI Tree
↓
Component Graph
↓
Dependency Graph
↓
Task Graph
↓
Patch
↓
Code
↓
Validation
↓
Tests

---

# Spec First

AI must always read and follow feature specifications before implementing code.

Implementation must not begin without understanding the feature spec.

---

# Small Scope Generation

AI must generate code in **small patches**.

Allowed operations:

create file
update specific function
add tests
add documentation

Large refactors are not allowed unless explicitly requested.

---

# Patch Rules

Never modify unrelated files.

Never modify existing code unless explicitly requested.

Prefer creating new files over editing many files.
